"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-paris-2024-2024-0724-1461515-olympics-security\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Kate Varley The organisers of the Paris Olympics have promised an \\\"unprecedented\\\" security operation in the city ahead of the official start of the games later this week, and indeed the signs are everywhere in the heart of the French capital.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 4, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.9992695002230001, \"rank\": 0.0007268395145948051, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}, {\"begin\": 5, \"end\": 11, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._F._Varley\", \"score\": 0.9999999994961399, \"rank\": 5.007961227048505e-10, \"text\": \"Varley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._F._Varley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C._F._Varley\"}, {\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.7926817539025005, \"rank\": 0.21996429533729295, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The organisers\", \"from\": 12, \"to\": 26}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 30, \"to\": 48}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"unprecedented\\\" security operation\", \"from\": 63, \"to\": 100}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 112}, {\"ngram\": \"the official start\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 140}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 153}, {\"ngram\": \"the signs\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Officials have said more than 45,000 police officers are being deployed, while a 6km anti-terrorism barrier has been erected along the banks of the River Seineahead of the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Officials\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 254}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 45,000 police officers\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6km anti-terrorism barrier\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"the River Seineahead\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police checkpoints and metal barriers are now a familiar sight in central Paris, while the enormous police deployment means an officer is never more than a few hundred feet away.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 614, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 510, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.771897137598256e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Police checkpoints\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 454}, {\"ngram\": \"metal barriers\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"a familiar sight\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"the enormous police deployment\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 553}, {\"ngram\": \"an officer\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rarely in peacetime has Paris experienced such high levels of security.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.771897137598256e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"peacetime\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"such high levels\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Friday's ceremony poses a particular challenge for authorities.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Friday's ceremony\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"a particular challenge\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"authorities\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike previous summer Olympics, it will not take place inside a stadium - instead, a flotilla of barges will carry thousands of athletes down the River Seine.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 901, \"end\": 912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"previous summer Olympics\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"a flotilla\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"barges\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To keep participants safe, France will impose a no-fly zone of 150km during the ceremony, while snipers will be deployed on the top of buildings along the route.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 942, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9166833704760239, \"rank\": 0.09072260218119262, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"participants\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"a no-fly zone\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"150km\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"snipers\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1059}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Access to the Seine within that 6km route has now been blocked off to anyone without a special pass or QR code to enter.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1092, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999956066858, \"rank\": 4.393385981254424e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Access\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"that 6km route\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1154}, {\"ngram\": \"a special pass\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"QR code\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For as long as the closing ceremony has not finished, we need to remain vigilant,\\\" Tony Estanguet, president of the Paris 2024 Organising Committee, said earlier this week.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1284, \"end\": 1298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}, {\"begin\": 1317, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.104812660859103e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Security is our number one priority for Paris 2024,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1416, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.104812660859103e-16, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Security\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"our number one priority\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Marc Hecker, a security analyst at the French Institute for International Relations, the main security threats facing Paris ahead of the Olympics come from \\\"jihadis and other terrorist groups from the far right,\\\" while nonviolent activists also pose a challenge to the smooth running of the games.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\", \"score\": 0.9999999999749889, \"rank\": 2.4807520385780442e-11, \"text\": \"Hecker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.771897137598256e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a security analyst\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1484}, {\"ngram\": \"the French Institute\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"International Relations\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1536}, {\"ngram\": \"the main security threats\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"jihadis\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"other terrorist groups\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"the far right\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"nonviolent activists\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1692}, {\"ngram\": \"a challenge\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"the smooth running\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1736}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities are particularly stringent about cybersecurity, amid concerns that hackers will attempt to access information from the main France 2024 system.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9166833704760239, \"rank\": 0.09072260218119262, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Authorities\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"cybersecurity\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"hackers\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite those security challenges, Mr Hecker believes Paris is ready.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\", \"score\": 0.9999999999749889, \"rank\": 2.4807520385780442e-11, \"text\": \"Hecker\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florian_Hecker\"}, {\"begin\": 1963, \"end\": 1968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.771897137598256e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those security challenges\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"They have been preparing for years now, and it will be an amazing deployment of security forces for several weeks.\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing deployment\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"security forces\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"several weeks\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will be around 45,000 policemen and gendarme for the opening ceremony, plus more than 10,000 soldiers and 20,000 private security officers.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around 45,000 policemen\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"gendarme\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 10,000 soldiers\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2214}, {\"ngram\": \"20,000 private security officers\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The idea, of course, is to maximise the protection, and to minimise the risk.\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The idea\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"the protection\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2331}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, you cannot annihilate the risk.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will always be one.\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the idea is not to accept defeat against terrorism by abandoning this magnificent setting.\\\"\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"defeat\", \"from\": 2434, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"terrorism\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"this magnificent setting\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We need your consent to load this rte-player contentWe use rte-player to manage extra content that can set cookies on your device and collect data about your activity.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your consent\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"this rte-player contentWe\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2555}, {\"ngram\": \"rte-player\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"extra content\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"cookies\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"your device\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2630}, {\"ngram\": \"data\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2647}, {\"ngram\": \"your activity\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please review their details and accept them to load the content.Manage Preferences Around 1,000 officers will be on duty to protect Israel's football match against Mali, meanwhile, where protests are expected, French Interior Minister Gerald Darmanin said.\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2802, \"end\": 2808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.235242422467431e-14, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 2834, \"end\": 2838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mali\", \"score\": 0.996856509155428, \"rank\